Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base and M'Quve's fleet\Nare now at a standstill...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...as they hide in the floating debris\Nof the Texas zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,... unable to confirm\Neach other's precise location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Char and Sayla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Who's watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't mention It{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're no ordinary soldier, Lalah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck's on our side.\NThe air is escaping more slowly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry and get back to the Zanzibar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stay behind and stall the Gundam{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Right. But, Captain...\N- Lalah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,l keep telling you\Nthere's no need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hurry and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Char, the Red Comet... l believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm concerned about Amuro too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,... in this situation, the one who moves first\Nis at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro will be fine.\NHe's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... l just know, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Dellamin !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a clear advantage\Nin fighting strength. Let's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We're only up against one enemy,\Nbut it is a large warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we carelessly revealed ourselves now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Baromel has been attacked !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lieutenant Uragang !\N- Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you learn anything\Nwhile serving under Captain M'Quve?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Barom's ship\Nwill be here very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll wait until then.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. The other mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,... l can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a red mobile suit,\Nso the pilot could've been Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you, Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lalah ! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Char attacking me from the rear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was that a different enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be getting complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's pilot\Nmay be a Newtype as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My firing was accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But he dodged every shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from the side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This time from the front!\NYou're good, Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Char?\NWhere's he coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...just watch !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Char. l can read your moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you've gotta respond a little faster... !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Char... !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,l should've broken this thing in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,l won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've used up a lot of energy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,l almost had him, too... !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But would Char really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,l seriously doubt that pilot\Nfell for a dummy explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we able to get in touch\Nwith the White Base yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. The area has a high Minovsky particle\Ndensity, and with all the floating debris...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,l know all that.\NBut we still must...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait. Just a moment, sir.\N- ls it the White Base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Zeon high-speed heavy cruiser!\NDirection 08-32. Relative velocity, 007 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Point us toward the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a vessel approaching us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- A Federation Magellan-class battleship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Prepare for battle!\NRotate main cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights from possible combat\Ndetected at points A-1 7, B-33.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on Captain Barom's flight course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. Could it be Barom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All vessels! Abandon your present positions!\NProceed to specified coordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've detected the enemy fleet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading for the unconfirmed battle zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So they got impatient...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla! Launch the G-Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Job John, stand by in the Guncannon !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- White Base, proceed !\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're entering fleet combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Fighter, launching !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is coming from behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one panic! Fire all guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,l have you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they attacking with only one fighter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mega particle cannons!\NMain cannons! Missiles! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Large number of missiles incoming !\N- What about the anti-missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost too easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's frightening to see what happens\Nwhen the momentum has shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They got us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Turnabout 1 80 degrees.\NWe'll approach the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One vessel advancing from\Nthe unconfirmed battle zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a moment! We have it!\NIt looks like a Magellan-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Magellan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There might be enemy survivors inside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be cautious. I'll wait outside{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten a lot tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker. Where did you detect the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sir! Around Point N-5 in the C-Block.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceeding to N-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Omur! Sayla! Job! Stand by on the buggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Touchdown completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Omur! Sayla! Job!\NGo out and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to level 2 battle stations\Nuntil we find Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Kai standby in the Guncannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw. What's the status of the radio comm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw! What's the status of the radio comm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, it should be okay to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Job John here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Job John here! Come In, White Base!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ! Yes! White Base here, go ahead !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't located the Gundam yet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw, could you go see how Hayato's doing?\NHe must be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- Fraw. Have Vammas come up here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.\Nl understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla here. Sayla here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Go ahead, White Base.\N- Sayla?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's not Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, l just relieved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Have you found anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,l thought l told you to quit the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you've become a Petty Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Joining the Zeon military\Nto take revenge on the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your actions don't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you truly believe that your own brother\Nis such a petty man, Artesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...Who is she talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The things Jimba Ral told us\Nmight have been true after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man always used to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did your father, Lord Zeon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He did it for the the future of all mankind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...who are destinedypes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he suddenly fell ill{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and on his deathbed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...your father singled out Degwin Zabi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish someone like me\Nto be the next prime minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understood Lord Zeon's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He pointed out Degwin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}... to Iet us know that it was Degwin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why else would your father's allies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's why I had no choice buta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...on Earth under false identities{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why l entered Zeon, and went\Nfrom high school to military academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...was so l could get close to the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But Artesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown up a little since that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,l realized that even if\Nthe Federation defeats the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,... humanity won't achieve true peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why...?\N- Newtypes have appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean because Amuro's a Newtype?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Newtype?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not pleased that a Newtype\Nhas become my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll have to fight any way l can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimba Ral taught us that Newtypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...are the ideal towards which\Nthe entire human race should strive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, there should be no need\Nto make Newtypes your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Casval !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,l told you, I'll fight any way l can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Artesia, you must leave the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Trojan Horse?! You mean the White Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll leave you enough gold\Nto pay your way from here to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Earth and live out your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer the brother you once knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know why l wear this mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I've discarded my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Artesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider... my dear brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, Artesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,War doesn't suit you.\NLeave the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Casval, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Casval, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! What's the matter, Bright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ls Amuro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The static was awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. But l am worried about Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Casval, my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Br... Brother... !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. They've all been burned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\NI've never seen a machine like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a White Base buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!\NMs. Sayla has found Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't move, so we'll need the Gunperry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right! Send it out immediately!\N- Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmission from Wakkein.\NA Zanzibar-class warship is leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the port on the other side of Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the Gunperry launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go in the White Base and pick up\Nthe Gundam, Omur and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one Magellan-class ship!\NWe'll break through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. What exactly happened\Nwhile you were in Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah... Even my life has\Nits share of tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we've been able\Nto retrieve my Gelgoog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one enemy ship! Aim carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will be here soon to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hold our ground until then !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mirai, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Depart from the same port as the Zanzibar\Nand begin pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've detected a signal-emitting\Nobject near Shutter No. 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- ls it an explosive?!\N- l don't know. But it's very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! At a desperate time like this... !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Omur check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Doesn't look like it's an explosive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just trash !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant Wakkein !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That bastard Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Commandant Wakkein...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All l know is that the letter attached\Nto the case is addressed to you, Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto for Omur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea who it's from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,l have the right to inspect this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd rather you told me the contents\Nof the case, and who sent it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,l believe that the case is filled with gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And who sent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Char Aznable, the Red Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,l hope with all my heart\Nthat you'll fulfill your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To the gentle Artesia Som Deikun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...With love, from Casval Rem Deikun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear brother Casval...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear brother Casval...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla...or rather, Artesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...felt that as long as she could remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...she had followed her brother's back\Nalways calling out his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was there beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Would she never again be able to call him...\Nher brother Casval?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Before anyone knows it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...the war enters a new stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The phantom attacks\Nof one single mobile armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...confuse Amuro,\Ncausing the Gundam's functions to falter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NThe Newtype: Challia Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtype: Challia Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:54.20,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:59.20,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:09.42,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:14.34,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:18.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:24.35,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:28.94,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:39.24,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:54.20,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:59.20,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:09.42,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:14.34,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:18.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.97,0:24:24.35,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:28.94,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:39.24,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
